house-price-prediction/
├── backend/                        # Backend Folder (Flask API)
│   ├── app.py                      # Main Flask application
│   ├── models/                     # Trained models and scaler
│   │   ├── house_price_model.pkl   # Trained machine learning model
│   │   └── scaler.pkl              # Standard Scaler (for feature scaling)
│   ├── requirements.txt            # Python dependencies for backend
│   └── .gitignore                  # Ignore unnecessary files (e.g., .env, .pyc)
│
├── frontend/                       # Frontend Folder (HTML, CSS, JS)
│   ├── index.html                  # HTML structure for the app
│   ├── styles.css                  # Styles for frontend
│   └── script.js                   # JavaScript for handling form submission and API calls
│
├── data/                           # Data Folder
│   ├── train.csv                   # Training data (Ames Housing dataset)
│   └── test.csv                    # Test data (Ames Housing dataset)
│
├── utils/                          # Utility functions
│   └── preprocess.py               # Preprocessing steps (like handling missing values, encoding, etc.)
│
├── .gitignore                      # Ignore unnecessary files (e.g., .env, .pyc, etc.)
├── README.md                       # Project documentation and instructions
└── requirements.txt                # List of Python dependencies for the entire project
